ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 14, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rqt1665703148379.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rqt1665703148379.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rqt1665703148379.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rqt1665703148379\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Returns the <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.ValidationError</span> object containing the error information as provided during the previous <span class=\"keyword apiname\">showError</span> trigger.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"rqt1665703148379__topic_d127196e1_d127197e1_d127198e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rqt1665703148379__p_d127199e1_d127200e1_d127201e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Return</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FieldErrorContext</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">.</code>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">getError()</span>\n</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104rqt1665703148379_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"rqt1665703148379__codeblock_i31_vr5_cwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vError = 'Error: ' + this.getError().message ;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rqt1665703148379__section_w1213ab1b5b3_w1214ab1b5_w1215ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d940352e79\">Return Value</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rqt1665703148379__p_d127205e1_d127206e1_d127207e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword apiname\">getError</span> returns:</p>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"rqt1665703148379__parml_lzq_hs5_cwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">uniface.ValidationError</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Object if a validation error occurred. </dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">Null</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">If no error has occurred. </dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rqt1665703148379__section_w1216ab1b5b5_w1217ab1b5_w1218ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d940352e112\">Exceptions</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following exceptions may be thrown:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">uniface.InvalidDataObjectException</code></li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rqt1665703148379__section_w1219ab1b5b7_w1220ab1b5_w1221ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d940352e129\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rqt1665703148379__p_d127217e1_d127218e1_d127219e1\">Use the <span class=\"keyword apiname\">getError</span> function in the\n        showError and showClear web triggers to access the error number, message, and the incorrect\n        field value that caused the error.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rqt1665703148379__section_m1x_fkv_1dc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d940352e141\">Example: Using getError</h2>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104rqt1665703148379_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"rqt1665703148379__codeblock_vjy_qs5_cwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">webtrigger showError\njavascript\n \"use strict\";\n // this = the current field\n var vError = this.getError();\n var vLabel = this.getField().getLabel();\n var vErrorMsg = 'Error: ' + vError.message; \n if (vLabel) {\n vErrorMsg += '/n Location: ' + vLabel.getValue();\n } else {\n vErrorMsg += '/n Field: ' + this.getName();\n }\n vErrorMsg += '/n The incorrect value is: ' + vError.valueInError;\n alert(vErrorMsg);\n return true;\nendjavascript\nend</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/irg1665702783697.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.ValidationError</a><p>The uniface.ValidationError object provides access to the error number and message of a validation error on the server. It is returned by the FieldErrorContext.getError function when used in the showError and clearError web triggers.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/shk1665703139073.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.InvalidDataObjectException</a><p>Exception thrown if the object on which the function is called is no longer valid.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531747\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531747\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "getError() Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 14, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Returns the uniface.ValidationError object containing the error information as provided during the previous showError trigger. Return = FieldErrorContext . getError() Explain this code vError = 'Error: ' + this.getError().message ; Copy Return Value getError returns: uniface.ValidationError Object if a validation error occurred. Null If no error has occurred. Exceptions The following exceptions may be thrown: uniface.InvalidDataObjectException Description Use the getError function in the showError and showClear web triggers to access the error number, message, and the incorrect field value that caused the error. Example: Using getError Explain this code webtrigger showError javascript \"use strict\"; // this = the current field var vError = this.getError(); var vLabel = this.getField().getLabel(); var vErrorMsg = 'Error: ' + vError.message; if (vLabel) { vErrorMsg += '/n Location: ' + vLabel.getValue(); } else { vErrorMsg += '/n Field: ' + this.getName(); } vErrorMsg += '/n The incorrect value is: ' + vError.valueInError; alert(vErrorMsg); return true; endjavascript end Copy Related Links uniface.ValidationError The uniface.ValidationError object provides access to the error number and message of a validation error on the server. It is returned by the FieldErrorContext.getError function when used in the showError and clearError web triggers. uniface.InvalidDataObjectException Exception thrown if the object on which the function is called is no longer valid. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}